<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>وَالْيَمِين<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>غير الْمَرْدُودَة<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>تفِيد قطع الْخُصُومَة فِي الْحَال لَا بَرَاءَة<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>لذمة الْمُدَّعِي عَلَيْهِ<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
